rows.label: bf11840100_0030
rows.name:
There's a royal spirit cave in the Liberalitas
Archipelago. I'm going to seal this there.

rows.label: bf11840100_0050
rows.name: I have a favor to ask you guys.

rows.label: bf11840100_0055
rows.name:
I hear a unit from the resistance
evacuated to Speranza.

rows.label: bf11840100_0060
rows.name:
Tell them that when things settle down,
they should come to the Liberalitas Archipelago.
